### Prisma Express Backend API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

###

### 2. Get All Users
GET http://localhost:3001/users

###

### 3. Create a New User
POST http://localhost:3001/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 30
}

###

### 4. Create Another User
POST http://localhost:3001/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "age": 25
}

###

### 5. Get User by ID (replace {id} with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/users/1

###

### 6. Update User (replace {id} with actual user ID)
PUT http://localhost:3001/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "name": "John Updated",
  "age": 31
}

###

### 7. Delete User (replace {id} with actual user ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/users/1

###

### 8. Test Error - Get Non-existent User
GET http://localhost:3001/users/999

###

### 9. Test Error - Create User with Missing Fields
POST http://localhost:3001/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid@example.com"
}

